textAnnotations.description:
Gay, a little puzzled, went through
to the bac. Doc and hilyan well
sitting just inside having coffee.
"Come and join us and being your
boy friend,'" Dec called. No, Dec!"
tilgan remonstrated. They want to be
alone . " " I've booked a table at the
cate * ?2," Doc said, "they ale pocked
tonight so come and join us it
can't find a table for two.
you
